  "Hydrosphere and biosphere": "",
  "Geosphere and atmosphere": "",
  "Biosphere and hydrosphere": "",
  "A volcanic eruption is a geosphere-atmosphere interaction because material from Earth's interior (geosphere) is ejected into the atmosphere as ash, sulfur dioxide, and other gases that can affect weather and climate.": "",
