  "Lunar gravitational energy only": "",
  "Solar energy and internal geothermal energy": "",
  "Only solar energy": "",
  "Only geothermal energy": "",
  "Earth's systems are driven by two primary energy sources: external solar energy (powering weather, climate, the water cycle) and internal geothermal energy from radioactive decay (driving plate tectonics and volcanism).": "",
