  "The atmosphere creates currents without being affected in return": "",
  "Warm and cold currents redistribute heat, influencing atmospheric temperature and weather": "",
  "Ocean currents transport vast amounts of thermal energy around the globe, warming or cooling the atmosphere above them and influencing weather patterns, storm formation, and regional climates.": "",
