  "A natural part of the nitrogen cycle unaffected by humans": "",
  "The rock cycle": "",
  "Plate tectonics": "",
  "Cascading effects through interconnected Earth systems": "",
  "This eutrophication scenario demonstrates cascading effects: fertilizer on soil (geosphere) enters water (hydrosphere) through runoff, fuels algal growth (biosphere), and depletes oxygen, killing aquatic life. It illustrates systemic interconnection across spheres.": "",
